This project contains the sources for the Lucene - Thrift - Ruby blog.  If you want to run
the unit test, download lucene-thrift-example.tar.gz from the downloads link above.  
Extract the tar file then execute the runSearchTest.sh script.  You will need to have Java, Ruby and the 
thrift gem installed.  You don't have to have thrift installed or generate any code, all dependencies to run the test are included.
